sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant API as API Gateway
    participant Redis
    participant BullMQ
    participant Worker
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant Midtrans

    Note over Client,Midtrans: REGISTRATION FLOW
    Client->>API: POST /events/:id/register
    API->>Redis: DECR event:{id}:slots
    Redis-->>API: sisa_slot (>= 0 | < 0)
    alt sisa_slot < 0
        API->>Redis: INCR event:{id}:slots (rollback)
        API-->>Client: 409 SOLD OUT
    else sisa_slot >= 0
        API->>Redis: SET event:{id}:reservation:{uuid}<br/>{userId, eventId, status:"held"}<br/>EXPIRE 300
        API->>BullMQ: Enqueue create-order job<br/>{reservationId, eventId, userId}
        API-->>Client: 200 {reservationId, jobId}
    end

    Note over Client,Midtrans: WORKER: CREATE ORDER
    BullMQ-->>Worker: Dequeue create-order job
    Worker->>DB: BEGIN transaction
    Worker->>DB: INSERT Registration (status:"registered")
    Worker->>DB: INSERT Order (status:"pending", total_amount)
    Worker->>Midtrans: POST /snap (order_id, gross_amount)
    Midtrans-->>Worker: { snap_token, redirect_url }
    Worker->>DB: INSERT Payment (status:"pending", snap_token)
    Worker->>DB: COMMIT
    Worker-->>Client: (via WS/polling) { orderId, snap_token }

    Note over Client,Midtrans: MIDTRANS WEBHOOK
    Midtrans->>API: POST /payments/midtrans/webhook
    API->>DB: SELECT Payment WHERE provider_order_id
    DB-->>API: Payment record
    alt SUCCESS (settlement / capture)
        API->>DB: UPDATE Payment → status:"settlement"
        API->>DB: UPDATE Order → status:"paid", paidAt:now
        API->>DB: INSERT Ticket (ticket_code, qr_token)
        API->>Redis: DEL event:{id}:reservation:{uuid}
    else FAILED (deny / cancel / expire / failure)
        API->>DB: UPDATE Payment → status sesuai
        API->>DB: UPDATE Order → status:"failed"
        API->>Redis: INCR event:{id}:slots (release)
        API->>Redis: DEL event:{id}:reservation:{uuid}
    end
    API-->>Midtrans: 200 OK

    Note over Client,Midtrans: RECOVERY (Redis Restart)
    API->>DB: SELECT events.capacity - COUNT(registrations)<br/>WHERE status != 'cancelled'
    DB-->>API: sisa_slot
    API->>Redis: SET event:{id}:slots = sisa_slot
